extends /sites/CricketSquad/layouts/base.pug

block variables
    - const title = 'Privacy Policy – CricketSquad'
    - const description = 'Learn how CricketSquad handles your personal information. Our privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your data while you enjoy our fantasy cricket game.'

block content
    +Header()

    main
        section.container.privacy-policy
            h1 Privacy Policy for CricketSquad
            p At CricketSquad, we prioritize the protection of our users' privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines the types of information we collect, how we process it, and how we use it on our platform, cricket-squad.com.
            p If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, feel free to contact us.

            h2 Log Data
            p Similar to most websites, CricketSquad collects log data to monitor user activity on the platform. This data includes your IP address, browser type, Internet Service Provider (ISP), date and time of visit, the pages you view, and the number of clicks. This data is anonymous and is used for website analysis, administrative purposes, and demographic research.

            h2 Third-Party Services
            p We may use third-party services for analytics and website improvement. These services help us understand user interactions and enhance the user experience. However, they do not collect personally identifiable information.

            h2 Advertising Partners
            p Some of the advertisers on our platform may collect data to display relevant ads. Each of our advertising partners has its own Privacy Policy, which we recommend you review.

            h2 Privacy Policies of Advertising Partners
            p While we provide information about our advertising partners, we are not responsible for their practices. For more information about their Privacy Policies, please refer to their respective policies.

            h2 Children's Privacy
            p We are committed to protecting children’s privacy online. We encourage parents and guardians to monitor their children’s online activities and guide them through their experiences on the internet.

            p CricketSquad does not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 18. If you believe that your child has submitted such data on our platform, please contact us, and we will take the necessary steps to remove it.

            h2 Online Privacy Policy Only
            p This Privacy Policy applies solely to online activities and is valid for users who visit cricket-squad.com. It does not cover data collected offline or through other means.

            h2 Consent
            p By using our website, you consent to our Privacy Policy and agree to the associated Terms and Conditions.

            p If you have any further questions regarding our Privacy Policy, don’t hesitate to contact us.



    +Footer()